# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# Fateh Music Academy — Legacy course-slug redirects
#
# Every course page now lives at /courses/{slug}-course (see
# src/data/courses.js). Google has indexed the old, unsuffixed
# form of several of these URLs (e.g. /courses/guitar) from before
# the "-course" suffix was added, so those searches land on a 404.
#
# These 301s send both real visitors and Googlebot to the current
# page and teach Google's index the correct URL over time.
# https://developers.cloudflare.com/pages/configuration/redirects/
# ------------------------------------------------------------------

